line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                        \u003CdecoDesc>\n                            \u003CdecoNote>A togate male figure stands in the middle of the field, his head rising in the middle of line 2 and to the left of line 3 of the text; a pair of raised arms/hands bracket the text.\u003C/decoNote>\n                        \u003C/decoDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462281\">Lilybaeum\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/6542148\">Marsala\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>37.80355, 12.4379\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"-0200\" notAfter-custom=\"-0101\" evidence=\"archaeological-context\">2nd century BCE (Manni Piraino)\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\" when=\"1984\">Excavated in the via del Fante necropolis in 1984.\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">Photographed, Metcalfe, 2018-08-31\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n           